          </text>
          <text id="/covid_education/sneezing_coughing/sneezing_coughing_overview:label">
            <value>Do not cough near others. Always cough or sneeze into a tissue or your bent elbow. If you cough in your hands, wash your hands after with soap and water.</value>
          </text>
